          "type": "custom_faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Is this legit? Like I could actually win??",
            "answer": "<p>Yes! Since 2018 we have given away amazing prizes and we do NOT plan on stopping soon! Our Giveaways are 100% legal and backed by our administrator.</p><p>To see all of our Past Winners <a href=\"#\">click here!</a></p>",
